author: SuperCarlinBrothers
description:
Welcome to the GRAND FINALE of the 2025 J vs Ben season! We have clipped together every J vs Ben for the entire year so you can relive it all and find out who the grand champion is!  From the “In the Movies,” “Quotes Quizes,” and “Open Book,” formats we had a lot of curve balls this year.

We actually had so much footage this year we had to break it into 2 parts, so be on the look out for part 2 in a couple of days! (if you have finished this one by then!)

Huge thanks to all the quiz masters throughout the year! We could not make the show without you and look forward to all of your questions next year!

#SuperCarlinBrothers #HarryPotter

Written by: J & Ben Carlin
Edited by: Ethan Edghill

Super Carlin Brothers explore Harry Potter theories, Pixar connections, and all your favorite fandoms every week!
